Any criticism belongs in the criticism section, not in the description.
To describe the Neocatechumenal Way as a 'cult' is not only offensive but inaccurate.
NCW is not a sect or cult .it is not an organization but part of the Catholic Church..it is a reformation program to those who want to understand the value of their baptism.
